<div class="h-auto grid grid-cols-1 gap-8">
  <!-- Heading -->
  <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-800 mb-4">Investment Opportunities</h1>
  </div>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-8">
      <!-- Image -->
      <%= image_tag "roma_cube_3.png",
                    alt: "The Cube",
                    class: "rounded-lg shadow-lg w-3/4 max-w-2xl" %>

      <div>
        <b class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">
          Where visionaries invest, culture thrives, and innovation lives.
        </b>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4"><i> </i></p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Invest and seize the opportunity to be part of a landmark development in one of Mexico City’s most
          desirable districts. Discover The Cube—an architectural icon in the vibrant heart of Roma Norte.
          This eight-story masterpiece redefines modern luxury and functionality, offering an
          unparalleled blend of cultural innovation, business sophistication, and urban living.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Roma Norte thrives as a hub of culture and growth, making it a much sought-after destination
          for real estate investment. More than a building, The Cube is a bold architectural statement
          and a dynamic lifestyle destination poised to draw elite businesses, visionary creatives,
          and innovative entrepreneurs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 mt-28">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-8">
      <div class="mr-4">
        <b class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">
          Reasons to Invest
        </b>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4"><i> </i></p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <b>• Prime Location</b>: Nestled in Roma Norte—
            Mexico City’s beating heart of culture,
            cuisine, and creativity—The Cube stands
            at the iconic corner of Colima and Orizaba, surrounded by top-tier properties in
            one of the city’s most vibrant and visited
            neighborhoods.
          </div>

          <div class="mb-4">
            <b>• Sky-High Demand: </b> Businesses and creatives are clamoring for sleek, flexible
            spaces in Roma Norte. The Cube delivers
            with a cutting-edge design, offering the
            modernity and functionality the 21st century demands.
          </div>

          <div class="mb-4">
            <b>• Architectural Brilliance: </b>
            With its bold
            off-center design, The Cube isn’t just a
            building—it’s a future landmark, blending
            innovation and prestige while adding to
            the district’s rich architectural tapestry.
          </div>

          <div class="mb-4">
            <b>• Diverse Income Potential: </b>
            From its multi-level gallery and high-end retail to
            award-winning dining, a rooftop wine bar,
            state-of-the-art offices, incubators, a private club, and luxury living spaces, The
            Cube is a powerhouse of revenue-generating opportunities.
          </div>

          <div class="mb-4">
            <b>• Smart Investment: </b>
            Offering ROI in as little as 15 years, The Cube combines
            security, profitability, and the allure of one of
            the most desirable real estate markets in the largest Spanish-speaking city on
            the planet.
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>

      <%= image_tag "roma_cube_4.png",
                    alt: "The Cube",
                    class: "rounded-lg shadow-lg w-3/4 max-w-2xl" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
